content: Congratulations! You've completed the experiment. Thank you very much.
name: Instruction_end

content:
Welcome!


On each trial, you will hear a repeated word or tone with a ticking clock sound. Your job is to say whether the ticking clock is in time or out of time relative to the tone/word.
Please use earphones, earbuds or headphones while completing the task. Please adjust your volume to a comfortable sound level.
Now let's hear some clear examples of 'not in time' so you know what to listen for.
name: LandingWelcome

content:
Good job! Ok, let's move on to the real experiment now.

You won't see or hear the feedback in the following session.
